<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
	<!--#include virtual="../../front/common/meta.shtml"-->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/department.css">
	<style>
		.switch-list{padding-left: 40px;}
		.switch-list li{margin-bottom: 20px;width: 400px;color: #333;}
		.switch-btn{display: inline-block;width:60px;height:31px;float: right;background: url(/public/img/index/btn-on-off.png) no-repeat 0 0;vertical-align: middle;}
		.switch-btn-on{background-position: 0 -31px;}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<!--#include virtual="../../front/common/header.shtml"-->
	<div class="container">
		<!--#include virtual="../common/side.shtml"-->
		
		<div class="content">
			<h4 class="contentNav system-setupNav">
				系统设置
				<span class="navTab">
					<a href="news.shtml" index="0" class="currTab">角色互通</a>
				</span>
			</h4>
			<div class="otContent">
				<p class="mb20 mt20 pl20" style="font-size:16px;">各角色空间互通设置，互通的角色可以互相添加关注，然后相互查看最新动态。发布私信。进入对方空间。</p>
				<ul class="switch-list">
					<li>班级教师与学生间互动通<a class="switch-btn switch-btn-on" href="javascript:;"></a></li>
					<li>班级教师与学生家长间互通<a class="switch-btn switch-btn-on" href="javascript:;"></a></li>
					<li>校内教师与教师间互通<a class="switch-btn switch-btn-on" href="javascript:;"></a></li>
					<li>班级家长与家长间互通<a class="switch-btn switch-btn-on" href="javascript:;"></a></li>
					<li>班级学生与学生间互通<a class="switch-btn switch-btn-on" href="javascript:;"></a></li>
					<li>校内所有角色间互通<a class="switch-btn" href="javascript:;"></a></li>
					<li>全站所有角色间互通<a class="switch-btn" href="javascript:;"></a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
	<!--#include virtual="../../front/common/footer.shtml"-->
<script>
	$(".switch-btn").click(function(){
		if($(this).hasClass("switch-btn-on")){
			$(this).removeClass("switch-btn-on");
		} else {
			$(this).addClass("switch-btn-on");
		}
	});
</script>
</body>
</html>